---
import { FaUsers, FaLightbulb, FaHandsHelping } from 'react-icons/fa';
---

<section id="initiatives" class="py-20 bg-white">
  <div class="container mx-auto px-4">
    <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold text-center mb-12">Initiatives & Projects</h2>
    
    <div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-8 max-w-6xl mx-auto">
      <div class="bg-gray-50 p-8 rounded-lg shadow-md">
        <FaUsers className="w-12 h-12 text-primary mb-6" />
        <h3 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-4">Kenya Universities Students' Organization (KUSO)</h3>
        <p class="text-gray-700">
          As President of KUSO, Antony has revitalized the umbrella student body to advocate effectively for over 72 public institutions, 56 colleges, and 258 TVETs. Under his leadership, KUSO has spearheaded voter education drives, mental health awareness campaigns, and collaborations with key government agencies.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="bg-gray-50 p-8 rounded-lg shadow-md">
        <FaLightbulb className="w-12 h-12 text-primary mb-6" />
        <h3 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-4">Youth Advocacy Africa (YAA)</h3>
        <p class="text-gray-700">
          Antony founded YAA to equip young Africans with the tools, networks, and confidence needed to thrive. YAA focuses on career development, good governance, and employment opportunities. It also partners with secondary schools to mentor students and promote post-COVID-19 recovery programs.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="bg-gray-50 p-8 rounded-lg shadow-md">
        <FaHandsHelping className="w-12 h-12 text-primary mb-6" />
        <h3 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-4">Change the Narrative Campaign</h3>
        <p class="text-gray-700">
          A personal initiative that encourages peaceful and constructive engagement in student leadership. This campaign has successfully rebranded student movements as forward-thinking, solutions-oriented voices in national dialogues.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>